  <brief_title>Proof-of-Concept Study Assessing VNS Paired With Tones for Tinnitus</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Proof-of-Concept Pilot Study Assessing Vagus Nerve Stimulation (VNS) Paired With Tones for Tinnitus</official_title>
